{"pageProps":{"bookPath":"go","postPath":"go-if","post":{"title":"Go: if 语句","body":"<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\">\n<div id=\"toctitle\">目录</div>\n<ul class=\"sectlevel1\">\n<li><a href=\"#_基本_if_语句\">基本 if 语句</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#_带有初始语句的_if_语句\">带有初始语句的 if 语句</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#_ifelse\">if&#8230;&#8203;else&#8230;&#8203;</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\">\n<h2 id=\"_基本_if_语句\">基本 if 语句</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>就像 <code>for</code> 语句那样，<code>if</code> 语句的条件表达式不需要用括号圈住，而且后面的花括号不可省略。比如：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-go\" data-lang=\"go\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> x &lt; <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"negative\"</span>\n}</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\">\n<h2 id=\"_带有初始语句的_if_语句\">带有初始语句的 if 语句</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>就像 <code>for</code> 语句那样，<code>if</code> 语句可以以一个短语句开始，这个语句在每次条件判断前执行。其中声明的变量只在 <code>if</code> 语句的作用域内有效。比如：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-go\" data-lang=\"go\"><span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">pow</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">(x, n, lim <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">float64</span>)</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">float64</span></span> {\n\t<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> v := math.Pow(x, n); v &lt; lim {\n\t\t<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> v\n\t}\n\t<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> lim\n}</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\">\n<h2 id=\"_ifelse\">if&#8230;&#8203;else&#8230;&#8203;</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p><code>if</code> 语句后面可以带有一个 <code>else</code> 块。在 <code>if</code> 语句的短语句中声明的变量也可以在 <code>else</code> 块中访问。比如：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-go\" data-lang=\"go\"><span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">pow</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">(x, n, lim <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">float64</span>)</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">float64</span></span> {\n\t<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> v := math.Pow(x, n); v &lt; lim {\n\t\t<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> v\n\t} <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n\t\tfmt.Printf(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"%g &gt;= %g\\n\"</span>, v, lim)\n\t}\n\t<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> lim\n}</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","type":"adoc"},"book":{"title":"Go 基础","toc":[{"title":"基础","path":"go-basic"},{"title":"函数","path":"go-func"},{"title":"变量","path":"go-var"},{"title":"基本类型","path":"go-basic-types"},{"title":"字符串","path":"go-string"},{"title":"指针","path":"go-ptr"},{"title":"数组和切片","path":"go-array-slice"},{"title":"映射","path":"go-map"},{"title":"结构：struct","path":"go-struct"},{"title":"接口：interface","path":"go-itf"},{"title":"type 关键字","path":"go-type"},{"title":"for 语句","path":"go-for"},{"title":"if 语句","path":"go-if"},{"title":"switch 语句","path":"go-switch"},{"title":"defer 语句","path":"go-defer"},{"title":"并发","path":"go-concurrency"},{"title":"包和导入","path":"go-pkg-import"}],"path":"go"}},"__N_SSG":true}